Name: Cyborg Ninja vs. The Third Reich
About the game: Cyborg Ninja vs. The Third Reich is a 2D action platforming game! Players assume the role of CN000, a prototype cybernetic ninja made for the sole purpose of destroying The Third Reich. Infiltrate a Nazi military base and decimate their forces from within in this throwback to the 16 bit side scrolling glory days! 2D Side Scrolling Action Arcade Style Gameplay 12 Challenging Levels 4 Difficulty Modes Original Chiptune Soundtrack Get ready to kick some Nazi ass!!!
